The reason why the meeting of Tuesday and subsequent evaluations of the meeting by the participants were made with a minimum of claims or charges.
The philosophical differences between Obama and the Republicans are too large and are very deeply rooted as to suggest any rapid change in the climate that existed during the last two years.
